659
00:45:45.660 --> 00:45:49.581
[Ellie jadeando] ¡No. no! ¡Quédate conmigo!

660
00:45:49.664 --> 00:45:50.498
¡No!

661
00:45:53.084 --> 00:45:53.877
No.

662
00:45:58.465 --> 00:46:00.049
[Coates grita]

663
00:46:04.846 --> 00:46:05.680
[Ellie grita]

664
00:46:06.848 --> 00:46:09.184
